msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_GoatThief_Desc"
msgid ""
"A shepherd in Hateno Village named Koyin is\n"
"worried that monsters will make off with her\n"
"flock of sheep.\n"
"\n"
"According to her, the monsters in question\n"
"congregate at <1.se_co>Hateno Beach<2.re_co>. She won't\n"
"breathe easy until <3.se_co>every last<4.re_co> monster there\n"
"is defeated."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_GoatThief_Extermination"
msgid ""
"You defeated every last monster lurking\n"
"on Hateno Beach! The village is safe for\n"
"sheep at last.\n"
"\n"
"Go tell <1.se_co>Koyin<2.re_co> in Hateno Village that the\n"
"monsters will trouble her flock no more."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_GoatThief_Finished"
msgid ""
"You told Koyin that you cleared out the\n"
"monsters living on Hateno Beach. In return,\n"
"she gave you a handsome reward.\n"
"\n"
"You feel like you're getting along quite well\n"
"with Koyin now! Maybe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_GoatThief_Name"
msgid "The Sheep Rustlers"
msgstr ""

